quality PES available and to within 10 cm$^{-1}$\nfor more than 60 % of the modes. For the MP2 PESs only around 60 % of the NN +\nVPT2 frequencies were within 20~cm$^{-1}$ of the experiment, with outliers up\nto 150 cm$^{-1}$ compared with experiment. It is also demonstrated that the\napproach allows to provide correct assignments for strongly interacting modes\nsuch as the OH bending and the OH torsional modes in formic acid monomer and\nthe CO-stretch and OH-bend mode in acetic acid.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Mar 2021 15:24:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Mar 2021 08:46:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-15"}
